### Welcome
GET http://localhost:3000/

### Get all packages
GET http://localhost:3000/packages

### Get package by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/packages/69c1e245520ec755949dc0d0

### Find packages by type
GET http://localhost:3000/packages/findByType?type=adventure

### Create a new package
POST http://localhost:3000/packages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Tropical Getaway",
  "type": "beach",
  "destination": "Hawaii"
}

### Update a package by ID
PUT http://localhost:3000/packages/69c1e245520ec755949dc0d0
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Getaway",
  "type": "beach",
  "destination": "Maldives"
}

### Delete a package by ID
DELETE http://localhost:3000/packages/69c1e245520ec755949dc0d0

