### Get all reviews
GET http://localhost:3000/reviews

### Get review by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/reviews/69c1e245520ec755949dc0d0

### Search reviews by comment
GET http://localhost:3000/reviews/findByReview?q=amazing

### Create a new review
POST http://localhost:3000/reviews
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "destination": "Hawaii",
  "rating": 5,
  "comment": "Amazing trip, highly recommend!",
  "author": "Jane Doe"
}

### Update a review by ID
PUT http://localhost:3000/reviews/69c1e245520ec755949dc0d0
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "destination": "Hawaii",
  "rating": 4,
  "comment": "Great trip but a bit crowded.",
  "author": "Jane Doe"
}

### Delete a review by ID
DELETE http://localhost:3000/reviews/69c1e245520ec755949dc0d0

